					"type": 23,
					"value": "Load BGO_Main_A. Debug book \"Quest Flags and Options\" -> Act3 -> Ironhand Gnomes -> Setup a predefined company of gnomes -> 1. Set up Oppress Scene.\r\nDebug Book -> Go To Region -> Act3 -> WYR -> Ironhand gnomes hideout.\r\nFind merchant gnome and talk to him. If a crime dialog is started, mention Barcus or Wulbren or \"I'm here to trade\" option."
